      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior looks great, though you will find some minor surface scratches and a few small rock chips on the hood from highway driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and some faint scuffing on the plastic door sills. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and is ready for its next owner with no immediate repairs needed.",
