      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. Mechanically, it starts and runs consistently, but you should expect some typical wear-and-tear such as minor fluid seeps and a suspension that is beginning to feel soft. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, small door dings, and some fading on the clear coat, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It is a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation who doesn't mind putting in a little cosmetic work or dealing with minor maintenance items soon.",
