      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six masterpiece. The engine pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from a recent valve adjustment and a preemptively addressed VANOS system. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a reinforced rear subframe to handle the lateral G-forces this chassis is capable of. It features a factory limited-slip differential and an unmolested suspension geometry that preserves its neutral handling balance. While showing honest signs of use, this M3 remains a sharp, driver-spec machine with impeccable mechanical integrity.",
